text: Mohd Hazwan Zainun (born 31 December 1987, in Kedah) is a Malaysian footballer currently playing as a midfielder for MISC-MIFA. Known as "Pak Leh" by fans, Hazwan is a product's of Kedah President Cup squad and was promoted to senior team for season 2007–08. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent Category:Malaysian footballers Category:People from Kedah Category:Living people Category:Perlis FA players Category:MISC-MIFA players Category:Association football midfielders
